{"tid":818173,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[城哥又贏]外電：長建研分拆部分英國資產倫敦上市","createTime":"2018-09-14T02:27:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T15:45:59.000Z","uid":57424,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1d2962697256c4e93ee481f6809199a6d67e4451","tid":818173,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T02:27:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=320178\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D320178&d=AAikRAnnkpmqLFbgyV%2BMLLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=d01f777b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D320178&h=3c6632fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=320178</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】外電報道，長江基建正考慮分拆部分英國資產於倫敦上市。<br />\n<br />\n彭博引述消息指，長建正與投資銀行討論將部分英國資產在倫敦上市的各種選項，探討透過一個數十億美元的基金持有長建部分英國資產上市。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士說，長建仍在討論上市的架構和分拆哪些資產，亦有可能不會進行分拆。<br />\n<br />\n長建在英國的資產包括英國電網、水務公司和鐵路資產等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n永遠都行先人一步<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b9b87bd5ca5a3717d0c1c47761f42cbebd870f5","tid":818173,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T15:31:32.000Z","msg":"唔夠CASH？"},{"pid":"0514f296d7cce855a7a3dc85726920d69335dc53","tid":818173,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b9b87bd5ca5a3717d0c1c47761f42cbebd870f5","tid":818173,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T15:31:32.000Z","msg":"唔夠CASH？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T15:33:27.000Z","msg":"澳洲放生收購apa 條件之一"},{"pid":"9b13f9edb9cd172efe6e0d7950bc2b1fe4bdf88b","tid":818173,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0514f296d7cce855a7a3dc85726920d69335dc53","tid":818173,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b9b87bd5ca5a3717d0c1c47761f42cbebd870f5","tid":818173,"uid":68728,